                     <interp inst="t18230514-101-person910" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at Aldgate. I was by this shop, and saw a man behind me stand by Whyte's door; he reached up his arm, took the bacon, and ran towards Butler's-buildings. I cannot say who it was.</p>
